00:34:12.679 --> 00:34:15.310
and I was curious to hear the
origin story of that book,

00:34:15.310 --> 00:34:20.370
same as how you're describing
how "Crooked" came about.

00:34:20.370 --> 00:34:22.679
AUSTIN GROSSMAN: That has
an origin story, as it were.

00:34:22.679 --> 00:34:24.389
"Soon I Will Be
Invincible" is about what

00:34:24.389 --> 00:34:26.460
it's like to be a
supervillain-- basically what

00:34:26.460 --> 00:34:28.770
is it like to be Lex Luthor.

00:34:28.770 --> 00:34:30.920
What is it like on the inside?

00:34:30.920 --> 00:34:34.600
What is it like when you go
home and have to make yourself

00:34:34.600 --> 00:34:37.150
breakfast in your
secret fortress?

00:34:37.150 --> 00:34:40.212
I have to say-- I mean,
that was my first book.

00:34:40.212 --> 00:34:42.670
I wrote it when I was in grad
school, when I was supposedly

00:34:42.670 --> 00:34:44.820
going to be an
English professor.

00:34:44.820 --> 00:34:45.960
It's about a lot of things.

00:34:45.960 --> 00:34:47.595
It's probably about being
a graduate student, where

00:34:47.595 --> 00:34:49.170
everyone tells you
how smart you are

00:34:49.170 --> 00:34:52.280
and then they just
totally step all over you.

00:34:52.280 --> 00:34:54.840
It's about just the
infuriated feeling

00:34:54.840 --> 00:34:58.540
that you're incredibly
smart and the world

00:34:58.540 --> 00:35:00.970
is just laughing at you.

00:35:00.970 --> 00:35:04.480
And it's was also about
getting up in the morning

00:35:04.480 --> 00:35:06.070
and doing it again.

00:35:06.070 --> 00:35:09.040
Because any supervillain
is like Wile E. Coyote.

00:35:09.040 --> 00:35:13.520
They come back, and they think
it's going to work this time.

00:35:13.520 --> 00:35:16.380
And that was, for
me, an affirmation

00:35:16.380 --> 00:35:17.773
of the human spirit.

00:35:20.400 --> 00:35:24.079
And also because no one was
going to write-- at the time,

00:35:24.079 --> 00:35:25.870
no one was going to
write "Watchman" again.

00:35:25.870 --> 00:35:27.750
I just wanted to
read more "Watchman"

00:35:27.750 --> 00:35:29.500
and I was going to
have to write it myself

00:35:29.500 --> 00:35:30.990
if it was going to happen.

00:35:30.990 --> 00:35:35.440
And then of course they
did, which is even sadder.

