00:43:49.280 --> 00:43:51.280
He just forced us
to acknowledge it.

00:43:51.280 --> 00:43:58.390
I mean, Warren G. Harding
was really the-- Teapot Dome

00:43:58.390 --> 00:43:59.220
Scandal.

00:43:59.220 --> 00:44:02.910
I mean, Harding was really
